'''金貓屬'''（[[学名|学名]]：''Catopuma''）是[[猫科|猫科]]下的一[[属_(生物)|属]]，包含[[亚洲金猫|亚洲金猫]]和[[婆罗洲金猫|婆罗洲金猫]]两个[[物种|物种]]<ref name="Catsg2017">{{cite journal |last1=Kitchener, A. C. |last2=Breitenmoser-Würsten, C. |last3=Eizirik, E. |last4=Gentry, A. |last5=Werdelin, L. |last6=Wilting, A. |last7=Yamaguchi, N. |last8=Abramov, A. V. |last9=Christiansen, P. |last10=Driscoll, C. |last11=Duckworth, J. W. |last12=Johnson, W. |last13=Luo, S.-J. |last14=Meijaard, E. |last15=O’Donoghue, P. |last16=Sanderson, J. |last17=Seymour, K. |last18=Bruford, M. |last19=Groves, C. |last20=Hoffmann, M. |last21=Nowell, K. |last22=Timmons, Z. |last23=Tobe, S. |year=2017 |title=A revised taxonomy of the Felidae: The final report of the Cat Classification Task Force of the IUCN Cat Specialist Group |journal=Cat News |issue=Special Issue 11 |pages=36−37 |url=https://repository.si.edu/bitstream/handle/10088/32616/A_revised_Felidae_Taxonomy_CatNews.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2018-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730142355/https://repository.si.edu/bitstream/handle/10088/32616/A_revised_Felidae_Taxonomy_CatNews.pdf?sequence=1&isAllowed=y |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，它们一般体呈红棕色，头部有明显的斑纹<ref name="VigorsHorsfield">{{cite journal |last1=Vigors, N. A. |last2=Horsfield, T. |year=1827 |title=Descriptions of two species of the genus ''Felis'', in the collections of the Zoological Society |journal=The Zoological Journal |volume=III |issue=11 |pages=449–451 |url=https://archive.org/details/zoologicaljourna318271828sowe/page/450}}</ref><ref name="Hodgson1831">{{cite journal |last1=Hodgson |first1=B. H. |year=1831 |title=Some Account of a new Species of Felis |journal=Gleanings in Science |volume=III |issue=30 |pages=177–178 |url=https://archive.org/details/gleaningsscienc3/page/176}}</ref>。两种金猫早在 490－530 万年前[[婆罗洲|婆罗洲]]与邻近岛屿还未分离时便已分化<ref name="Johnson1999">{{cite book |last1=Johnson, W. E. |last2=Ashiki, F. S. |last3=Menotti Raymond, M. |last4=Driscoll, C. |last5=Leh, C. |last6=Sunquist, M. |last7=Johnston, L. |last8=Bush, M. |last9=Wildt, D. |last10=Yuhki, N. |last11=O'Brien, S. J. |last12=Wasse, S. P. |last-author-amp=yes |year=1999 |chapter=Molecular genetic characterization of two insular Asian cat species, Bornean Bay cat and Iriomote cat |editor=Vasser, S. P. |title=Evolutionary Theory and Process: Modern perspectives. Papers in Honour of Eviatar Nevo |publisher=Kluwer Academic Publishing |location=Dordrecht |pages=223–248 |isbn=9780792355182 |chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=FTtrd9cl8tAC&pg=PA223 |access-date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726162818/https://books.google.com/books?id=FTtrd9cl8tAC&pg=PA223 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，它们最近的亲属是[[云猫|云猫]]（石纹猫）， 约 940 万年前云猫与金猫分化<ref name="johnson+al">{{Cite journal |last1=Johnson |first1=W. E. |last2=Eizirik |first2=E. |last3=Pecon-Slattery |first3=J. |last4=Murphy |first4=W. J. |last5=Antunes |first5=A. |last6=Teeling |first6=E. |last7=O'Brien |first7=S. J. |title=The Late Miocene Radiation of Modern Felidae: A Genetic Assessment |year=2006 |doi=10.1126/science.1122277 |journal=Science |volume=311 |issue=5757 |pages=73–77 |pmid=16400146 |url=http://home.ncifcrf.gov/ccr/lgd/mammal%20pdfs/MS545_Johnson_Science.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527223854/http://home.ncifcrf.gov/ccr/lgd/mammal%20pdfs/MS545_Johnson_Science.pdf |archive-date=2010-05-27 |bibcode=2006Sci...311...73J }}</ref>。

金猫属由[[俄国|俄国]]学者[[尼古拉·谢韦尔佐夫|尼古拉·谢韦尔佐夫]]在 1858 年以 ''Felis moormensis'' 为[[模式种|模式种]]建立<ref name="Severtzow1858">{{cite journal |last1=Severtzow |first1=M. N. |year=1858 |title=Notice sur la classification multisériale des Carnivores, spécialement des Félidés, et les études de zoologie générale qui s'y rattachent |journal=Revue et Magasin de Zoologie Pure et Appliquée |volume=X |pages=385–396 |url=https://archive.org/stream/revueetmagasinde10soci#page/386/mode/2up}}</ref>，该模式种由[[英国|英国]]学者 [[Brian_Houghton_Hodgson|Brian Houghton Hodgson]] 在 1831 年根据一只捕获自[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]的亚洲金猫命名<ref name="Hodgson1831">{{cite journal |last1=Hodgson |first1=B. H. |year=1831 |title=Some Account of a new Species of Felis |journal=Gleanings in Science |volume=III |issue=30 |pages=177–178 |url=https://archive.org/details/gleaningsscienc3/page/176}}</ref>，当时被归为[[猫属|猫属]]（''Felis''）的一种，现被归为亚洲金猫的北方[[亚种|亚种]]。

